{"tid":1377454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱發夢喺前線中椒，從心底感激勇武","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:40.000Z","uid":281692,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f64a61c00096bef9cf1d9b27378768a1b1b160d","tid":1377454,"uid":281692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"今日第一次發夢上前線，本身已經聞到啲椒味，行前啲，頭盔中彈，再行前啲，好多粒催淚彈飛過黎，眼，頸，手都有事，好辛苦，流晒眼水，好在即刻有人幫我淋生理鹽水，好快無事。<br />\n<br />\n我以前唔明點解勇武要咁樣行動，發完呢個夢之後，我終於明白到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勇武係<span style=\"color: red;\">保護</span>緊和理非</strong></span><br />\n如果無咗勇武，和理非一擊即散，亦都唔可以維持示威到今日。<br />\n<br />\n和理非要多啲感激勇武嘅付出！"},{"pid":"2bfc469262a5746f805b21719914fda5dcb1af7a","tid":1377454,"uid":15421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"發夢炸話？<br />\n怕咩呀"},{"pid":"7667e27ac22c2f5493c6539da9b20b306573cc58","tid":1377454,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cca4d0c3f20e82364ae57d1c0d6136ae8d52f54","tid":1377454,"uid":281692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bfc469262a5746f805b21719914fda5dcb1af7a","tid":1377454,"uid":15421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"發夢炸話？<br />\n怕咩呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"夢醒嗰陣兩行眼睙"},{"pid":"1694f2b6c58e96ad9cf4eaea84c728358d64cf47","tid":1377454,"uid":118787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:06:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6399bcb8ac139fc50885c8cf3026ac039ece4cb3","tid":1377454,"uid":15945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:06:51.000Z","msg":"發夢記得買齊裝呀 夢入面都唔好做負累"},{"pid":"656a3956556f80ad1535034357419cd949206c68","tid":1377454,"uid":211993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51b5e8